<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1938-03-15T07:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1938-03-15T07:00:00-05:00" n="462" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d462">
                    <note rend="inline" type="source">863.00/1475: Telegram</note>
                    <head><hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Austria</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Wiley</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss></hi></head>
                    <opener>
                        <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Vienna</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1938-03-15T13:00:00+01:00">March 15, 1938—1
                            p.m.</date><lb/>[Received March 15—11:50 a.m.]</dateline>
                    </opener>
                    <p>86. New press chief has just confirmed to the Legation that Austrian Foreign
                        Minister turned over affairs of Ministry this morning to Ribbentrop who
                        arrived last night.</p>
                    <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Wiley</hi></signed></closer>
                </div>
                </body></text></TEI>